Installing a React App

---> npm install create-react-app -g

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

						Creating a React App

---> npx create-react-app [React App Name]

Then go into the newly created React App folder and start the project

---> npm start

/public ---> All the static files are kept like html,css,javascript etc...
/src ---> All the react code will be kept here

